      "upgrade_patterns": "UUPS proxy pattern intended for IdentityStaking (implementation includes UUPSUpgradeable and overrides _authorizeUpgrade). Upgrade.sol is a sample new implementation for testing upgrades. No Diamond pattern present.",
      "access_control_structure": "Role-based access control via AccessControlUpgradeable. DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE is granted in initialize() to initialAdmin and is the admin for roles by default unless changed (not changed here). PAUSER_ROLE granted to initialAdmin in initialize(). SLASHER_ROLE and RELEASER_ROLE granted to provided arrays. pause/unpause restricted to PAUSER_ROLE. slash restricted to SLASHER_ROLE. release restricted to RELEASER_ROLE. UUPS upgrades restricted to DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE via _authorizeUpgrade. AccessControl management entrypoints (grantRole/revokeRole/renounceRole) are inherited and externally callable per OZ implementation.",
      "inventories_note": "No Diamond proxy detected; no cross-facet storage mapping applicable."
